name: Navy Trooper Vesden
Lore: 'Counterintelligence agent assigned by ISB. Operates sensors designed to protect the control bunker from infiltration.',
Text: 'If present with a Scomp link when Never Tell Me The Odds just reached the top of your Reserve Deck, may ''shield'' (add 3 to destiny number of) one of your characters at each location for remainder of turn.',
